{"word":"G5265 - ὑποδέω - hypodéō - hoop-od-eh'-o - Bind on","slug":"G5265","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑποδέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>hypodéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>hoop-od-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Bind on"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C5;&#x0314;&#x03C0;&#x03BF;&#x03B4;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - hupodeo&#x0304;</b> - <i>hoop-od-eh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G5259\">G5259</a> and <a href=\"#/G1210\">G1210</a>; to <i>bind under</i> one&rsquo;s feet, that is, <i>put on</i> shoes or sandals: - bind on, (be) shod."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G5266\">G5266</a>"}]}